The paper discusses semi-supervised learning using deep neural networks and focuses on improving discriminative power when a large portion of labels are absent. This topic is closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
